<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>78 minutes or 1 hour and 18 minutes. Sample response: I started at 10:30 and jumped 30 minutes to 11:00, 30 more minutes to 11:30, 15 minutes to 11:45, and then 3 minutes to 11:48. I jumped a total of 78 minutes.</li>
      <li>11:15 a.m. Sample response: <m>55 - 40 = 15</m></li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


